title: Why doesn't Dunkey voice a league character?
body: If anyone is curious, Videogamedunkey is a famous youtuber that is popular due to his league and video games videos. His voicing is what makes his videos funny and interesting. So here's an Idea, why doesn't Dunkey voice a league champion? Just imagine for a second having a champion with Dunkey's voice.

replies.body: He could voice the Teemo rework
Most popular youtuber or most popular league youtuber? because pewdiepie is most popular youtuber games/no games
